		<item>Series II : Hotel Morenci Financial and Payroll Records, 1904-1919
		  </item> 
		<item>Series III: Payroll and Time Books, 1882-1911</item> 
	 </list> 
  </arrangement> 
  <scopecontent encodinganalog="520"> 
	 <head>Scope and Content Note</head> 
	 <p>Financial journals, payrolls, time books, and ore and freight records
		related to mining company operations. Includes financial records of Hotel
		Morenci (1904-1913) and Frisco Ranch (1909-1913). </p> 
  </scopecontent> 
